title: Number of births in Norway 2008 to 2018
summary: In general Number of live births has fallen over the Year.

Number of live births is slightly decreasing from 2010 to 2011, roughly constant from 2011 to 2012, slightly decreasing from 2012 to 2013, roughly constant from 2013 to 2016, and finally gradually decreasing from 2016 to 2017.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Number of live births, about 61442.0 was reported at Year 2010
Minimum Number of live births about 56633.0 was reached at Year 2017
